messages.message: This is an issue in Prod: in _Settings > clicking Workspaces > click on Org name_ takes the user to blank screen
There's a bug fix for this that's merged in but not deployed :persevere: I'm going to try to fix some stuff via postman requests
:raised_hands:  nice job on the quick turn around

It actually didn't work to fix it via postman request. The issue happens when we deactivate users without removing them from the org first. I tried to remove them from the org via API but the API doesn't allow it when they are deactivated.

The good news is a) this will be fixed in tonight's prod deployment b) you can still get to this table if you don't go to workspaces first and c) this shouldn't be a problem for our multitenant customers because they aren't able to deactivate users.
